l onstage chat with Marvell CEO Matt Murphy at Computex.</p><p style=3D"mar=
gin:10px 0">Huang highlighted Marvell=E2=80=99s essential role in AI data c=
enters =E2=80=94 specifically its networking chips, custom silicon, and opt=
ical tech that move massive amounts of data between thousands of chips.</p>=
<h3>What makes MRVL special?</h3><ul><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Data ce=
nter business now makes up ~76% of Marvell=E2=80=99s total revenue (up from=
 much lower levels a couple of years ago).</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:1=
0px 0">Nvidia invested $2 billion in Marvell earlier this year.</p></li><li=
><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Pre-surge market cap was ~$192 billion. Reachin=
g $1 trillion would still require roughly a 5x increase.</p></li></ul><p st=
yle=3D"margin:10px 0">Huang=E2=80=99s comment lit the stamp of approval for=
 Marvell to spike. MRVL has gone from basically nothing in my portfolio to =
2.7%. </p><p></p></div></td></tr>
